{"id": 1464, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得如今的广告对“年轻人”都有哪些误解？", "description": "快别瞎说了，“年轻人”可不像你想的那样。（题图来自：Stinkyinky Jess ​​​​）", "record_count": 6396, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170120150227ywZxCGuoXe6SU9DK.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-24T03:00:54Z", "options": [{"id": 157952, "content": "追星", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 873168}, {"id": 158208, "content": "认为年轻人总是只看重当下", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903251}, {"id": 157697, "content": "燃你妹啊燃，烧不死你", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722457}, {"id": 157698, "content": "什么独具匠心，在我眼里都是祝你降薪", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722457}, {"id": 157699, "content": "世界还没见过就谈世界观", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910586}, {"id": 157955, "content": "觉得自己很懂年轻人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279847}, {"id": 214276, "content": "70后情怀，80后钱，90后开心……这话是70后说的吧？90后特么就没情怀？90后特么不要钱？情怀和钱不都是为了开心？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729453}, {"id": 157700, "content": "严格划分80 90  00后。", "image": null, "praise_count": 781, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913605}, {"id": 157701, "content": "作为一个资深广告人，其实也不是很懂手机广告里那些年轻人动不动发表一些很装逼的个性宣言，事实上都不是年轻人会说的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 455, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416515}, {"id": 192517, "content": "网吧“包夜”一说有歧义", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004746}, {"id": 157702, "content": "“勇敢做自己”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155259}, {"id": 157703, "content": "整容广告铺天盖地，审美跑偏，大家都爱网红整容脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567382}, {"id": 157705, "content": "拔萝卜", "image": "img/option/option/20170124121639idfk4L2Ze7UMGvKJ.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 909654}, {"id": 157961, "content": "拜金、崇洋、文青", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765001}, {"id": 158473, "content": "渐渐的背离传统", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893413}, {"id": 167177, "content": "要么特有活力要么特宅 要么特乖要么特叛逆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937694}, {"id": 157706, "content": "年轻 就要不一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 50917}, {"id": 157962, "content": "90后都是非主流……啊，不好意思，90后已经老了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475929}, {"id": 158730, "content": "因为现在那些扯淡的广告滥用字词，我看哪天新华字典也得改写", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 561632}, {"id": 157707, "content": "年轻人不都有这些特点吗？不存在太多误解", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531245}, {"id": 157963, "content": "大多应该都没什么钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902227}, {"id": 157708, "content": "最大的误解是那些广告人以为自己还年轻", "image": null, "praise_count": 256, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666750}, {"id": 157709, "content": "年轻人跟父母说话都是撒娇", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819794}, {"id": 157965, "content": "以为自己束缚于牢笼，殊不知自己早已驾凌于规则之上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914579}, {"id": 158221, "content": "以为给90后做的创意，80后来执行，70后拍的板，60后出的钱。都没意识到现在已经是00后的世界了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915463}, {"id": 160013, "content": "“青春，再不疯狂就老了”。这不该是说疯狂的去玩，无意义的“疯狂”。青春该疯狂的追求，奋斗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919652}, {"id": 158478, "content": "说年轻人不疯狂了就不是年轻人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915859}, {"id": 157711, "content": "咬着一帮都快26，7的90后叫年轻人（？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254456}, {"id": 158479, "content": "认为年轻人都是一样的，你们年轻人怎样怎样...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915859}, {"id": 159247, "content": "年轻人越来越更懂得，越长大越孤单……", "image": "img/option/option/20170129001817eok7rd9RHphlGqSm", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918087}, {"id": 159503, "content": "年轻人的生活又快乐又丰富多彩 弄得我们好像不是人似的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871043}, {"id": 157712, "content": "年轻人总很少能坚持点什么，撑不住", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914323}, {"id": 159504, "content": "不需要你懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 734809}, {"id": 157713, "content": "不知天高地厚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914326}, {"id": 158993, "content": "为我们提供了越来越多的可望而不可及的生活方式。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902773}, {"id": 157714, "content": "没有人理解", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058479}, {"id": 158226, "content": "有个性，做自己,其实他们不安又迷惘，随波逐流", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915476}, {"id": 157971, "content": "用了他的东西就是独特的，就是真实的自己?", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 848137}, {"id": 157716, "content": "叛逆的一代", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770560}, {"id": 157972, "content": "我\n21岁", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602979}, {"id": 161556, "content": "说起“给力”，想起14年，我高三，开大会，校领导的发言中一分钟一个“给力”，听到吐！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924772}, {"id": 157717, "content": "很有钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707022}, {"id": 158489, "content": "“年轻无极限”。年轻人也有困顿、忧愁啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806410}, {"id": 157723, "content": "年轻人都很疯狂。吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 909974}, {"id": 158491, "content": "说走就走旅行，旅行是刚需什么的。无比作…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773654}, {"id": 157980, "content": "我只是想证明我也是年轻人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456449}, {"id": 157981, "content": "年轻人并没有什么特别", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914799}, {"id": 159261, "content": "年轻人不是一定都会活力满满笑嘻嘻的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918187}, {"id": 254749, "content": "超前消费的模式感觉适合所有人……啥玩意儿？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666198}, {"id": 206878, "content": "热情奔放啊，酒吧夜店彻夜狂欢啊，放荡不羁啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039157}]}